title: Keepin' it 1947: Jon Favreau & Dan Pfeiffer On What Went Wrong for Democrats
description: The co-hosts of The Ringer's hit podcast, "Keepin' It 1600" join Chuck for a special co-pod to talk about the continuing aftershocks of the 2016 election and what it means for Democrats in the future.
